snippet.title: Realm of the Fallen Gameplay Cut
snippet.description:
This is a cut playthrough of two levels from my game, Realm of the Fallen. The game is now available for purchase for the Quest 2 and Quest 3. A PCVR version will be released on Steam in a few weeks. Full playthrough: https://youtu.be/mEf3jOZJdbw
